Lagaan: Once Upon a Time in India;;93;;95;;PG;;The year is 1893 and India is under British occupation. In a small village, the tyrannical Captain Russell (Paul Blackthorne) has imposed an unprecedented land tax on its citizens. Outraged, Bhuvan (Aamir Khan), a rebellious farmer, rallies the villagers to publicly oppose the tax. Russell offers a novel way to settle the dispute: he challenges Bhuvan and his men to a game of cricket, a sport completely foreign to India. If Bhuvan and his men can defeat Russell's team, the tax will be repealed.;;History,Drama,Romance;;Ashutosh Gowariker;;2001;;Aamir Khan,Gracy Singh,Rachel Shelley,Paul Blackthorne,Suhasini Mulay,Kulbhushan Kharbanda,Raghuvir Yadav,Rajendra Gupta,Rajesh Vivek,Shri Vallabh Vyas,Javed Khan,Raj Zutshi,Akhilendra Mishra,Pradeep Rawat,Daya Shankar Pandey,Yashpal Sharma,Amin Hajee,Aditya Lakhia,A. K. Hangal,John Rowe;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lagaan_once_upon_a_time_in_india